OL,7,FBut now he's told ITV News he would
OL,8,Fhand it back if it meant full and fair
OL,9,Fcompensation for all those still
OL,10,Ffighting for the money they are owed.
OL,12,F"If it was a choice between the
OL,13,Fknighthood and the financial redress
OL,14,Ffor all of the subpostmasters, I know
OL,15,Fwhich one I'd take," he said.
OL,17,FHe also suggested delays in
OL,18,Fcompensation payments to
OL,19,Fsubpostmasters could be a deliberate
OL,20,F'ploy' to encourage claimants to
OL,21,Fsettle for lower figures.
