OL,7,FThe Post Office told us those costs
OL,8,Freflect the "huge scale of the
OL,9,Fscandal" and its duty to support the
OL,10,Flong-running public inquiry.
OL,12,FFormer Post Office boss Paula
OL,13,FVennells' own sizable legal fees are
OL,14,Fsaid to be paid by the Post Office's
OL,15,Fdirectors' insurance scheme.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, former subpostmaster Janet
OL,18,FSkinner, who was wrongfully imprisoned
OL,19,Ffor three months in 2007, despairs of
OL,20,Fthe delay in agreeing to a settlement.
