OL,7,FThe Post Office told ITV News: "We are
OL,8,Ftruly sorry for the suffering caused
OL,9,Fto so many people by Post Office's
OL,10,Fpast actions. We recognise that
OL,11,Fvictims of the scandal and their
OL,12,Ffamilies cannot move on until full
OL,13,Fredress has been paid and both Post
OL,14,FOffice and Government are committed to
OL,15,Fdoing so as quickly as possible."
